Description: PEAK PERFORMERS is a temporary employment firm.
Full Description: PEAK PERFORMERS is a temporary employment firm. We are located in Austin, Texas, and we serve the State of Texas and other Central Texas governmental jurisdictions. And we specialize in employing people who have a disability. But you dont have to have a disability to be hired by us.  We service over 800 job classifications with the State of Texas, from entry level administrative support through highly skilled accountants, IT professionals, program administrators and many more. Again, we are a temporary employment company. Governments dont make hiring promises, so we dont either.  We assume you are looking us over because you are searching for work. So a logical question might be What kind of people do you hire? Well, the answer is in our name. We hire Peak Performers. Regardless of the skill set, we hire people (disabled or not) who have distinguished themselves by being reliable, consistent, productive and trustworthy. Distinguished by doing what they say they will do, when they say they will do it.  Our customers are dollar conscious public officials who have a set amount of work that must be completed within a specified time frame. And we are here to help them accomplish their goals. And you could be too, if youre a Peak Performer. If you too, are a person who does what you say you will do, when you say you will do it, then we want you.  Helping people find good jobs. Helping employers find good people. Helping people succeed. Thats who we are.
